{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"82746124ee","title":"周恩来给毛泽东林彪的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba46c3342d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":14,"articleId":"82746124ee","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对港台关系","id":"1f3b70f4a2","type":"主题"},{"name":"工商交通和财政","id":"1ffce755c0","type":"主题"},{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"黄永胜","id":"440b5f1bc1","type":"人物"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7ab122f08f","type":"title","text":"周恩来给毛泽东林彪的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82746124ee","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46c5396207","type":"paragraph","text":"主席、林彪同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82746124ee","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36d15def9f","type":"paragraph","text":"对广州交易会虽有五点指示发出，但据黄永胜报告，情况较紧，而军管会又难于控制。因此，今晨在解决内蒙问题后，特约外贸部和外贸学院两造反派商谈，他们愿派人去协助解决。考虑到目前院校和机关造反派多忙于内争，因而影响了广州交易会各公司、各馆的内部领导，并与各地方造反派形成派别，如不立即劝阻，对明（15）日开幕极为不利。我现定今晨7时同黄永胜同志飞广州，亲往解决此事，如顺利，今夜可飞回。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82746124ee","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1f6127938","type":"paragraph","text":"胡老（指胡志明）今晨5时抵穗，住从化，如有空，当去看他一下。如抽不出工夫，即为他组织当地会诊。因目前各医院多难互相调动，非打一招呼，不易保密。谨报，请转中央文革一阅。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82746124ee","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f9e889f895","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82746124ee","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"988fdebf73","type":"paragraph","text":"四月十四，六时","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"82746124ee","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}